name: PRuntime v2.1.0
body:
## Enhancements

* Upgraded SubXT to 0.28 and Polkadot to v0.9.43.
* Introduced pink runtime 1.1 and upgraded pink-extension-runtime to 0.4.4.
* Added support for batch HTTP requests, query signed in EIP-712, and configurable RA timeout and retries.
* Enabled trust-dns as resolver for outgoing HTTP.

## Fixes

* Resolved issues causing infinite restarts, memory leaks in logging, HTTP ABI incompatibility, and sidevm restart stucks.

## Other Changes

* Increased brk max size to 256M in pruntime and storage value limit to 1MB in pink.
* Merged deposit() and contract call() into a single call in pink-runtime.
* Introduced a safe handover feature and made parallelism for query in pruntime configurable.

## What's Changed
* Upgrade SubXT to 0.28 by @jasl in https://github.com/Phala-Network/phala-blockchain/pull/1244
* pruntime: Increase brk max size to 256M by @kvinwang in https://github.com/Phala-Network/phala-blockchain/pull/1231
* Fix non-first GK infinite restart issue by @kvinwang in https://github.com/Phala-Network/phala-blockchain/pull/1283
* Sidevm scheduler: Update wakers for ready tasks by @kvinwang in https://github.com/Phala-Network/phala-blockchain/pull/1282
* pruntime: Introduce pink runtime 1.1 by @kvinwang in https://github.com/Phala-Network/phala-blockchain/pull/1279
* pruntime: Don't call mallinfo on non-gnu targets by @kvinwang in https://github.com/Phala-Network/phala-blockchain/pull/1290
* Use Rust stable channel by @jasl in https://github.com/Phala-Network/phala-blockchain/pull/1289
* pink: Support for batch HTTP request by @kvinwang in https://github.com/Phala-Network/phala-blockchain/pull/1280
* Upgrade wamser to 3.3 by @kvinwang in https://github.com/Phala-Network/phala-blockchain/pull/1301
* pink: Add API driver_history by @kvinwang in https://github.com/Phala-Network/phala-blockchain/pull/1305
* pruntime: Configurable RA timeout and retries by @kvinwang in https://github.com/Phala-Network/phala-blockchain/pull/1321
* sidevm: Allow writing to stdout and stderr by @kvinwang in https://github.com/Phala-Network/phala-blockchain/pull/1325
* pruntime: Fix memory leak in logging by @kvinwang in https://github.com/Phala-Network/phala-blockchain/pull/1318
* Upgrade to Polkadot v0.9.43 by @jasl in https://github.com/Phala-Network/phala-blockchain/pull/1313
* pruntime: Don't panic in RA by @kvinwang in https://github.com/Phala-Network/phala-blockchain/pull/1332
* pink-runtime(internel): Merge deposit() and contract call() into a single call by @kvinwang in https://github.com/Phala-Network/phala-blockchain/pull/1333
* pruntime: Event chain by @kvinwang in https://github.com/Phala-Network/phala-blockchain/pull/1304
* pink: Enlarge storage value limit to 1MB by @kvinwang in https://github.com/Phala-Network/phala-blockchain/pull/1341
* Bump pink-extension-runtime to 0.4.4 by @kvinwang in https://github.com/Phala-Network/phala-blockchain/pull/1343
* pruntime: Fix crash due to HTTP ABI incompatibility (bug not exists in 2.0.1) by @kvinwang in https://github.com/Phala-Network/phala-blockchain/pull/1344
* pruntime: Support for query signed in EIP-712 by @kvinwang in https://github.com/Phala-Network/phala-blockchain/pull/1345
* eip712: Put more info on the signing panel by @kvinwang in https://github.com/Phala-Network/phala-blockchain/pull/1353
* Safe handover (Don't load system state in --safe-mode-level=2) by @kvinwang in https://github.com/Phala-Network/phala-blockchain/pull/1360
* pruntime: Configurable parallelism for query by @kvinwang in https://github.com/Phala-Network/phala-blockchain/pull/1364
* pruntime: Enable trust-dns as resolver for outgoing http by @kvinwang in https://github.com/Phala-Network/phala-blockchain/pull/1367
* pRuntime: Fix sidevm stucks at restart by @kvinwang in https://github.com/Phala-Network/phala-blockchain/pull/1371

**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/Phala-Network/phala-blockchain/compare/pruntime-v2.0.1...pruntime-v2.1.0

Thanks to @jasl and @kvinwang for their contributions.
